               <p>Fifth Middlesex Jury - Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>388. 
               <persName id="t18280110-133-defend870" type="defendantName">
                  MARTIN 
                  MOORE
               <interp inst="t18280110-133-defend870" type="surname" value="MOORE"></interp>
